        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>arrived
            <a name="encounter-status-arrived"> </a>
          </td>
          <td>Arrived</td>
          <td>The Patient is present for the encounter, however is not currently meeting with a practitioner.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
